function ajaxFileUpload(){$("input[type=submit]").ajaxStart(function(){$(this).prop("disabled",true)}).ajaxComplete(function(){$(this).prop("disabled",false)});$("#loading").ajaxStart(function(){$(this).show()}).ajaxComplete(function(){$(this).hide()});$.ajaxFileUpload({url:"base64.php",secureuri:false,fileElementId:"fileToUpload",dataType:"json",success:function(a){if(typeof a.error!="undefined")if(a.error!="")alert(a.error);else{var b=a.msg;if($("#mimetype").is(":checked"))b=a.mime+b;$("#output").val(b).select();var d=a.size,c=a.msg.length,e=Math.round((c/d-1)*100);$("#resultstats").html("Size increased from "+d+" to "+c+" ("+e+"%)")}},error:function(c,b,a){alert(a)}});return false}